{
  "slug": "agent-reviews",
  "name": "Agent Reviews",
  "type": "plugin",
  "description": "Manage GitHub PR review comments. Automatically triage, fix, and respond to review findings.",
  "longDescription": "Ships **3 skills** and a CLI (`agent-reviews`) for resolving PR review comments in a two-phase workflow: fix all existing issues, then poll for new ones until quiet.\n\n- **`resolve-reviews`**: All comments (human + bot)\n- **`resolve-agent-reviews`**: Bot comments only (Copilot, Cursor Bugbot, CodeRabbit, Sourcery, Codacy, SonarCloud)\n- **`resolve-human-reviews`**: Human comments only\n\nEach skill evaluates findings as true/false positives, fixes real bugs, dismisses false positives with explanations, and replies to every comment. Includes watch mode that polls until reviewers go quiet.",
  "compatibility": [
    "claude"
  ],
